{"id":"bd456de0528236945d7c5b8f72c6c8d808f75e1c2080dc010a67fee089cb5219","source":"support-chat","type":"conversation","payload":{"messages":[{"role":"user","content":"We're seeing way fewer compiled memories than we expected on the dispatch-automation subjects. ~5 memories per 100 episodes."},{"role":"assistant","content":"That ratio means heuristic compilation. For structured shipment events you'll want STATEWAVE_COMPILER_TYPE=llm — typically ~2× density on operational data. Heuristic compiler under-extracts from non-conversational episode shapes."},{"role":"user","content":"Okay, switching to llm."},{"role":"assistant","content":"Once flipped, run a one-time recompile on existing subjects so old episodes get re-extracted. Recompile is idempotent — no duplicates."}]},"metadata":{"imported_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783210+00:00","original_subject_id":"_build_demo_pack_demo-support-agent","imported_from_export_id":null},"provenance":{"imported_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783202+00:00","original_subject_id":"_build_demo_pack_demo-support-agent","imported_from_export_id":null,"content_hash":"bd456de0528236945d7c5b8f72c6c8d808f75e1c2080dc010a67fee089cb5219"},"created_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783613+00:00"}
{"id":"958d65b15c45c9a5f419cbf9aac798f9e134d488d66c90c0bbc19e134f203a9b","source":"support-chat","type":"conversation","payload":{"messages":[{"role":"user","content":"Quick check — what's the recommended way to backfill 6 months of historical shipment events into Statewave?"},{"role":"assistant","content":"Use POST /v1/episodes/batch with up to 200 episodes per call, parallelized 4-wide. At your projected ~3M backfill volume that's ~6 hours. Set last_compiled_at on each batch so the compiler doesn't re-process old data on every call. Want a runnable Python async script using your subject scheme?"},{"role":"user","content":"Yes please."},{"role":"assistant","content":"Sending an async script that uses AsyncStatewaveClient and your hooks.northwind-logistics.fr webhook pattern for progress notifications. mypy --strict clean."}]},"metadata":{"imported_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783210+00:00","original_subject_id":"_build_demo_pack_demo-support-agent","imported_from_export_id":null},"provenance":{"imported_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783202+00:00","original_subject_id":"_build_demo_pack_demo-support-agent","imported_from_export_id":null,"content_hash":"958d65b15c45c9a5f419cbf9aac798f9e134d488d66c90c0bbc19e134f203a9b"},"created_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783598+00:00"}
