{"id":"caca74485dd90aa9d9b160f83731da3668de94a76f0bf94452021cbdcdb2d06f","source":"support-chat","type":"conversation","payload":{"messages":[{"role":"user","content":"We've been seeing /v1/context time out for over four hours. Posted in the channel earlier — nobody picked up."},{"role":"assistant","content":"Apologies — the EU on-call rotation didn't catch this and it took until US hours for someone to reach you. That's a first-response SLA breach on #4937 and we'll issue a service credit. On the technical side: 30s timeouts on /v1/context point at pgvector index pressure. Can you confirm subject_id has >50k memories?"},{"role":"user","content":"It does — one of our long-running fleet subjects."},{"role":"assistant","content":"Recommend splitting fleet subjects into per-region or per-quarter scopes; ranking is fine, but unbounded subject growth slows the vector probe. I'll send a runbook."}]},"metadata":{"imported_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783210+00:00","original_subject_id":"_build_demo_pack_demo-support-agent","imported_from_export_id":null},"provenance":{"imported_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783202+00:00","original_subject_id":"_build_demo_pack_demo-support-agent","imported_from_export_id":null,"content_hash":"caca74485dd90aa9d9b160f83731da3668de94a76f0bf94452021cbdcdb2d06f"},"created_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783553+00:00"}
