{"id":"82f37e2077ba671177abbc2be213ef1778b7e601564846cdea2eb2c3359b9871","source":"support-chat","type":"conversation","payload":{"messages":[{"role":"user","content":"Login is sluggish for some users today. Not broken, just slow."},{"role":"assistant","content":"Could be SSO-adjacent again — Northwind hit a SAML cert issue last week (#4821). Checking if this is a regression: are the affected users on a specific IdP group? If only some users are slow, it's more likely a session-cache problem than SSO; if everyone is slow, I'd look at SSO first."},{"role":"user","content":"Only users in our 'drivers' group, actually."},{"role":"assistant","content":"Then it's almost certainly session-cache pressure on that group, not SSO. I'll save this as a distinct symptom from #4821 so we don't conflate them in future."}]},"metadata":{"imported_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783210+00:00","original_subject_id":"_build_demo_pack_demo-support-agent","imported_from_export_id":null},"provenance":{"imported_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783202+00:00","original_subject_id":"_build_demo_pack_demo-support-agent","imported_from_export_id":null,"content_hash":"82f37e2077ba671177abbc2be213ef1778b7e601564846cdea2eb2c3359b9871"},"created_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783462+00:00"}
{"id":"be9922a76bae631cb2eec79b96c2bea769c5efd394daee647be1b70f6a679b7f","source":"ticket-system","type":"ticket_resolved","payload":{"ticket_id":"4821","resolution":"Customer rotated expired SAML signing cert in Okta and uploaded the new public cert. SSO restored ~30m after upload. No code change required.","first_response_minutes":2,"sla_resolution_breached":false,"time_to_resolution_minutes":45,"sla_first_response_breached":false},"metadata":{"imported_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783210+00:00","original_subject_id":"_build_demo_pack_demo-support-agent","imported_from_export_id":null},"provenance":{"imported_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783202+00:00","original_subject_id":"_build_demo_pack_demo-support-agent","imported_from_export_id":null,"content_hash":"be9922a76bae631cb2eec79b96c2bea769c5efd394daee647be1b70f6a679b7f"},"created_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783447+00:00"}
{"id":"86c732df8406cb31e70d87fbc31e65dd9e5b01386dedfdadad2a82de30ff62ee","source":"support-chat","type":"conversation","payload":{"messages":[{"role":"user","content":"Urgent — nobody at Northwind can log in. SAML SSO returns 'invalid signature' for every user."},{"role":"assistant","content":"Opening this as ticket #4821 at high severity. 'Invalid signature' across all users is almost always a signing-cert problem on the IdP side — either expired or rotated without updating us. Could you check the cert expiry on your Okta SAML app first?"},{"role":"user","content":"Cert expired this morning. Auto-rotation didn't fire."},{"role":"assistant","content":"Confirmed cause. Rotate the cert in Okta and upload the new public cert in Account → SSO → Identity Provider. Average rotation time on a fresh cert is ~30 minutes for new sessions to clear; existing sessions stay valid."}]},"metadata":{"imported_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783210+00:00","original_subject_id":"_build_demo_pack_demo-support-agent","imported_from_export_id":null},"provenance":{"imported_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783202+00:00","original_subject_id":"_build_demo_pack_demo-support-agent","imported_from_export_id":null,"content_hash":"86c732df8406cb31e70d87fbc31e65dd9e5b01386dedfdadad2a82de30ff62ee"},"created_at":"2026-05-06T15:25:18.783432+00:00"}
